        <briefdescription>
<para>Scalar Q15 dot product. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Each product is widened to int32_t before accumulation into int64_t to avoid overflow. Correct for all Q15 inputs and any n ≤ 2^33. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
